{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-4","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Vežba 4","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kao što ste naučili, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">repetir</span> znači ponoviti nešto. Kada dodate zamenicu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lo</span>, vi se odnosi na nešto što je već pomenuto. Ta zamenica zauzima mesto specifične stvari (reči, broja, adrese e-pošte, itd.). Dakle:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Repetir</span> = ponoviti.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Repetirlo</span> = Ponovi to.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Repetirlo</span> Koristi se kada je \"nešto\" već poznato iz konteksta. Taj primer važi i za druge glagole:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes escribirlo?</span> - Da li možeš da pišeš?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedes decirlo otra vez?</span> - Možete li to ponoviti?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk i kompletnuj sledeću rečenicu.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Lo</span> To je glagol direktnog objekta koji se koristi za zamenu već poznate stvari u razgovoru. Kada je spojen sa infinitivom, stvara jednu reč:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">repetir</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lo</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">repetirlo</span> - Ponovi to.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">escribir</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lo</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">escribirlo</span> - Napisati to.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">decir</span> + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">lo</span> → <span class=\"highlighted-text\">decirlo</span> - Reci to.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ova struktura je uobičajena kada slušalac već razume na šta se \"to\" odnosi.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-4"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>¿Puedes repetirBLANK?</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"lo","feedback":"<p>Ovo je zamenica koja zauzima mesto za nešto što je već pomenuto.</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room2.png","characters":[{"character":"Mateo","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_mateo_camila_phone_number_dialogue.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":15.53,"finishTimestamp":16.68},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.15,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Puedes repetirlo?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Mateo","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.65,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","dashedName":"task-4","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-basic-personal-details","module":"es-a1-module-sharing-your-personal-details","block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-5"